Database Design
There are 4 key entities:
Users
Messages
Chat Rooms
Private Chats

Users Collection
Fields: id, username, status, createdAt
Description: Stores user information.

ChatRooms Collection
Fields: id, roomName, members, createdAt
Description: Stores chat rooms information

PrivateChat Collection
Fields: id, user1, user2, createdAt
Description: Stores information about private chats between 2 users.

Messages Collection
Fields: id, senderId, chatRoomId, privateChatId, content, timestamp
Description: Stores messages with reference to a private chat or group chat
